Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.66,0:01:20.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,谢谢大家 谢谢各位\N{\fs90}Greetings. Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.73,0:01:23.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,欢迎收看GrandTour\N{\fs90}Welcome to The Grand Tour
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.36,0:01:25.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,在这周的节目中\N{\fs90}And in this week's program
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.84,0:01:28.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,我开着辆轿车\N{\fs90}I drive a saloon car
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.70,0:01:34.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯开着餐车\N{\fs90}James drives a catering lorry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.55,0:01:39.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,理查德来了场械斗\N{\fs90}And Richard has a knife fight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.86,0:01:40.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,让我们来跳舞吧\N{\fs90}Let's dance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:45.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,这些稍后播出 但是首先\N{\fs90}That is all to come, but first of all
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.34,0:01:48.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,先说说这集的拍摄地 这里是南非\N{\fs90}let me talk you through where we are. It's South Africa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.75,0:01:52.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,那儿远处 可以看见约翰内斯堡\N{\fs90}Over there, in the distance, you can see Johannesburg
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.07,0:01:56.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,这个地方 被誉为人类的摇篮\N{\fs90}But this place here is called The Cradle of Humankind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.73,0:01:59.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为考古学家认为\N{\fs90}Now it's called that because archaeologists have determined
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.86,0:02:01.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,就在这个地点\N{\fs90}it was on this very spot
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.47,0:02:04.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,猿猴进化成了人类\N{\fs90}that mankind separated from the ape
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.11,0:02:10.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧 我是说\N{\fs90}Well, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:15.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,看到了嘛 我们还没开始呢\N{\fs90}We haven't even begun
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:17.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,-怎么了 -说句公道话\N{\fs90}-What?  -Be reasonable
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.18,0:02:20.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,你是会穿袜子 但是除此之外\N{\fs90}You've learnt to put socks on,but other than that, mate...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:23.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,我只想显得有深度一点 好嘛\N{\fs90}Listen, I'm trying to be profound here, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.35,0:02:25.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,-你继续 -之所以要显得有文化\N{\fs90}-Carry on, carry on.  -I'm trying to be profound
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.21,0:02:26.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为这是起源之地\N{\fs90}Because this is ground zero
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.80,0:02:29.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是人类历史开始的地方\N{\fs90}This is where all of human history began
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.43,0:02:32.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,所有来到这里的人 都像回到了家\N{\fs90}Anyone who comes here, it's like coming home
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.20,0:02:34.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,-杰里米  -又怎么了\N{\fs90}-Jeremy.  -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.70,0:02:38.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们中某些人从猿进化到人花了多久\N{\fs90}How long has it taken some of us to evolve from being apes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:40.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,花了有\N{\fs90}It's taken
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.12,0:02:43.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,两百万 零一百\N{\fs90}two million and a hundred...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:54.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,你在家看的 可能会奇怪为什么所有人都在鼓掌\N{\fs90}You at home may be wondering why everybody here is applauding
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.50,0:03:00.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是因为当其余的人类\N{\fs90}but it's because while the rest of mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:04.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,正在试图去掌握算术的概念\N{\fs90}has managed to grasp the concept of arithmetic
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:07.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,南非的总统 雅各布 祖玛\N{\fs90}the President of South Africa, Jacob Zuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:09.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,我该怎么说呢 他并没有掌握\N{\fs90}Well, how can I put this? He sort of hasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.72,0:03:12.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,这有个片段 给大家看看\N{\fs90}I've got a clip here to show you what I'm on about
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.12,0:03:17.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们在此宣布 我们的成员数据\N{\fs90}We announce that our membership figures
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:23.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,到达了 769\N{\fs90}stood at...769
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.16,0:03:24.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,800\N{\fs90}eight-hundred and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.98,0:03:29.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,700\N{\fs90}700...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.61,0:03:31.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,仔细听好了\N{\fs90}Listen properly
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.45,0:03:36.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,76万9千\N{\fs90}769 thousand
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.47,0:03:41.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,820\N{\fs90}820...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.63,0:03:48.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,我是说 说真的\N{\fs90}I mean, honestly
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:51.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,有趣的是\N{\fs90}The funny thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.63,0:03:56.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,雅各布 祖玛是个有争议的人物\N{\fs90}Jacob Zuma is a bit of a controversial figure here
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:59.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,他最近在家造了个游泳池\N{\fs90}He recently installed a swimming pool at his home
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.16,0:04:02.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,然后 因为是用纳税人的钱建的\N{\fs90}And then, because he'd used taxpayers' money to do that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:07.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,他说这其实是为防火而建的储水设施\N{\fs90}he said it was actually a water storage facility in case of a fire
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.21,0:04:10.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以 换句话说 如果他不小心着火了\N{\fs90}So, in other words, if he burst into flames
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:12.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,他可以跳进去自己灭火\N{\fs90}he can jump into it and put himself out
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:15.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,在一千……三百 秒里\N{\fs90}in ten hundred and... three hundred...seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:20.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,他还给自己买了辆自称的消防车\N{\fs90}He has also bought himself what he claims is a fire engine
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:21.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,这很可以\N{\fs90}Nice
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.87,0:04:25.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,他还买了一辆救护车\N{\fs90}He's also got himself an ambulance
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.50,0:04:27.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,是的 不能更小心了\N{\fs90}Yep. Can't be too careful
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.01,0:04:30.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,在南非驾驶汽车\N{\fs90}Motoring in South Africa
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:32.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,最大的问题就是野生动物\N{\fs90}Big problem here, of course, is the wildlife
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:35.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,你怎样才能准确地警告驾驶员\N{\fs90}because how do you accurately warn motorists
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.85,0:04:38.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,可能有个鹿状的东西在前方\N{\fs90}that there may be a deer-y thing ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.07,0:04:40.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,还可能被充满了氦气\N{\fs90}and it could be full of helium?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:43.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,有关部门尝试了下\N{\fs90}Well, the authorities have had a go
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:44.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们提出了这个标志\N{\fs90}They've come up with this as a sign
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:48.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,其实还不坏 只是他们把字打错了\N{\fs90}It's not bad, except they've got the word wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.36,0:04:53.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,什么情况啊\N{\fs90}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:54.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,这明明是错的\N{\fs90}It's wrong, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:56.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,-这才不是狒狒呢 -这才不是\N{\fs90}-It's not baboons  -No, it's not
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:58.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们从英国来的 都知道这不是狒狒\N{\fs90}We're from England. We know that's not a baboon
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.74,0:05:03.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,这里的狒狒其实是很危险的\N{\fs90}Baboons are actually very dangerous here
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.67,0:05:10.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,显然 它们比当地警察更会用枪\N{\fs90}Certainly, they've got a better idea of how to handle a gun than the local police
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:16.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,他竟然把这个当折凳用\N{\fs90}He's actually using that as a shooting stick
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:18.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们能回到节目中来了吗\N{\fs90}Shall we get on with the show?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.14,0:05:21.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,-好想法 好计划 -是的 开始吧\N{\fs90}-Yes, good idea. Good plan.  -Yes, let's
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:23.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,让我们从阿斯顿马丁开始\N{\fs90}And we start with Aston Martin
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:25.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为这个公司最近肯定开了一次会\N{\fs90}The company must have had a meeting recently
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:26.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,大老板一定拍板了\N{\fs90}and the bosses must have said
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:29.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,到下一部007电影上映还要好几年\N{\fs90}"It's gonna be a few years now until the next Bond film is out
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.56,0:05:31.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,那咱们阿斯顿马丁该干嘛\N{\fs90}"so what are we gonna do
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:33.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,才能在真空期抢几个头条呢\N{\fs90}at Aston Martin to generate some headlines in the meantime?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:35.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,因此他们决定\N{\fs90}And what they must have decided is
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.16,0:05:37.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,极尽所能的做好一辆车\N{\fs90}to make a car that is as good as a car can be
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.88,0:05:40.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们可不是说造赛车\N{\fs90}They weren't talking about making a racing car
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.01,0:05:43.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为比赛规定了引擎标准\N{\fs90}because in racing there are rules about how big the engine can be
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.03,0:05:44.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,准许使用哪种轮胎\N{\fs90}and what sort of tyres you can use
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:46.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且造的也不是公路车\N{\fs90}And they weren't talking about making a road car
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.81,0:05:49.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,不然就要遵守排气污染法规\N{\fs90}that would have to meet emissions regulations
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:51.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,在悬挂上用舒适的橡胶部件\N{\fs90}have comfy rubber bits in the suspension
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:53.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,所有这一切只会减慢速度\N{\fs90}And all that stuff would slow it down
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.32,0:05:58.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,是的 他们想造辆不受规则所限的车\N{\fs90}Exactly. They wanted to make a car that adhered to no rules and no regulations
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.81,0:06:00.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们确实做到了\N{\fs90}So they have
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.03,0:06:12.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,这就是成果\N{\fs90}This is what they came up with
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.96,0:06:21.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,它价值180万英镑\N{\fs90}It costs £1.8 million
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:25.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,它叫 火神\N{\fs90}And it's called the Vulcan
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:30.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,惊为天物 不是吗\N{\fs90}Spectacular, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.05,0:06:37.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,但不是很实用\N{\fs90}But not very practical
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:59.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦天呐\N{\fs90}Oh, God. Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.11,0:07:14.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,完蛋 我彻底卡住了\N{\fs90}Now I'm totally stuck
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.78,0:07:18.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦 可以了\N{\fs90}Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.63,0:07:23.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,你们会把这段切掉的对吧\N{\fs90}You will be able to edit this out, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.43,0:07:25.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,我才不想别人说我胖\N{\fs90}I don't want people thinking I'm fat
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.87,0:07:29.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,好了 我要挂上档\N{\fs90}Right. I'm gonna pop it into gear now
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:31.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,动静可能有点大\N{\fs90}You may hear this a little bit
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.45,0:07:38.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,踩离合器\N{\fs90}Er...foot on clutch
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.36,0:07:41.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,踩离合器\N{\fs90}Er...foot on clutch
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:46.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,接着就是给7升V12发动机点火了\N{\fs90}And now it's time to fire up the seven-litre V12
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.76,0:08:05.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,这很正常\N{\fs90}It's quite normal
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:20.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,出发以后 事情并没有转变\N{\fs90}When I got going, things didn't get much better
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:30.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,即使是低速 这里还是很吵\N{\fs90}Even at slow speeds, it is quite loud in here
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.21,0:08:33.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以我要戴着傻兮兮的麦克风\N{\fs90}which is why I'm wearing this silly face microphone
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.27,0:08:34.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,你们才能听到我\N{\fs90}so you can hear what I'm on about
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:40.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,这台车噪音最大的地方 居然不是引擎\N{\fs90}The noisiest part of this car, however, is not the engine
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:48.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是刹车声\N{\fs90}That's the brakes
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.72,0:08:55.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,这种噪音相当尖\N{\fs90}They are quite... They are quite squeaky
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.63,0:09:01.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,听上去像踩在小猪上\N{\fs90}It actually sounds like I'm stamping on a piglet
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:07.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,当你深踩油门 情况更糟了\N{\fs90}And things get worse when you put your foot down
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.27,0:09:17.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,我不会说这像被一头熊攻击\N{\fs90}I'm not going to say that it's like being attacked by a bear
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:18.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,确实不像\N{\fs90}because it isn't
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.65,0:09:22.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,但这仿佛 和熊共处一室\N{\fs90}But it is like being in a room with a bear
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.38,0:09:24.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,而它正准备攻击你\N{\fs90}that's thinking of attacking you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:29.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,当我把发动机旋钮转到这\N{\fs90}At the moment I've turned the engine down on this knob here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.47,0:09:31.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,转到它最低功率设置\N{\fs90}to its minimum setting
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:35.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,它只产生500马力\N{\fs90}It's only producing 500 horsepower
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:40.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以并不是速度吓人\N{\fs90}So it's not really the speed that's scary
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.54,0:09:41.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦老天\N{\fs90}Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.78,0:09:46.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,是这噪音 这粗糙度和这震动\N{\fs90}It's the noise and the harshness and the vibrations
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:54.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,这车的配置很低\N{\fs90}It's not a very well-equipped car either
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.35,0:09:56.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,比方说 车窗就没法降下来\N{\fs90}The windows don't wind down, for instance
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:09:58.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,车里也没什么可玩的\N{\fs90}There are no toys at all
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:02.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,方向盘也只有半个\N{\fs90}And you only get half a steering wheel
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:09.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,可是 你花的180万英镑\N{\fs90}However, there is one amazing thing
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.28,0:10:11.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,还是有个神奇的功能\N{\fs90}you get for your £1.8 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:15.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,它包含所有在你选择的赛道上\N{\fs90}An all-expenses-paid trip to a racetrack of your choice
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:17.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,由阿斯顿马丁的试车手\N{\fs90}where an Aston Martin test driver
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:19.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,教你怎么开这车的费用\N{\fs90}will teach you how to drive your car
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:23.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,不是用500匹的低功率调教\N{\fs90}not with the engine wound down to 500 horsepower
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:25.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,而是调高\N{\fs90}but with it turned up...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.24,0:10:27.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,到了极限\N{\fs90}...to the max.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:42.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的天 哈哈哈\N{\fs90}Holy cow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.51,0:10:51.93,字幕,,0,0,0,,发动机现在输出820匹马力\N{\fs90}The engine is now producing 820 horsepower
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.93,0:10:53.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,这速度\N{\fs90}And the speed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:55.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,简直无法想象\N{\fs90}just beggars belief
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.98,0:11:00.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,熊进入攻击模式\N{\fs90}The bear is in attack mode
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:05.59,字幕,,0,0,0,,数据显示 0到100\N{\fs90}The figures say it'll do 0-60
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.59,0:11:07.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,只需2.9秒\N{\fs90}in 2.9 seconds
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:12.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,带着这大尾翼最高速度都有335公里\N{\fs90}And has a top speed of 208 with that wing on the back
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:16.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,实际感觉要快太多了\N{\fs90}But it feels a hell of a lot faster than that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:18.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fs90}Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:28.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,你花钱买来的\N{\fs90}The other thing you get for your money
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.34,0:11:30.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,还有一大帮机械师\N{\fs90}is a squadron of mechanics
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:34.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,但可惜\N{\fs90}But sadly..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.49,0:11:37.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,买不来手刹\N{\fs90}not a handbrake
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:41.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧 你听我解释\N{\fs90}Right, what I've done now is I've taken... yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:44.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,我把方向盘拆了\N{\fs90}I've taken the steering wheel off
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.02,0:11:46.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,于是没法把它挂上档防溜车了\N{\fs90}so I can't put it in gear to stop it rolling away
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.37,0:11:48.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,老天\N{\fs90}Oh, God
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.64,0:11:59.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,当我最终停下车\N{\fs90}When I'd finally got it to stop
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:01.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,把车子举升起来\N{\fs90}the jacks were deployed
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.12,0:12:03.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,机械师就开工了\N{\fs90}and the mechanics set to work
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.56,0:12:07.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,这就是火神\N{\fs90}That's the thing about the Vulcan
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:10.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,尾翼角度 防倾杆 悬挂 刹车\N{\fs90}Wing angle, roll bar, suspension, brakes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.13,0:12:14.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,这些都能根据个人喜好来调整\N{\fs90}Everything can be adjusted to suit your personal taste
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.48,0:12:19.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,在装作知道他们在做什么后10分钟\N{\fs90}After ten minutes of pretending I knew what they were doing
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.22,0:12:21.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,我回到了赛道\N{\fs90}I was back on the track
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.81,0:12:26.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,车子感觉\N{\fs90}And the car felt...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.98,0:12:29.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,还是和之前一样疯狂\N{\fs90}just as bonkers as it had done before
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.34,0:12:34.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是 我不一样了\N{\fs90}However, I've changed
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.20,0:12:38.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,这车我开了\N{\fs90}I've been driving this thing now
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.05,0:12:40.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,记不清了 三四个小时\N{\fs90}I don't know, three or four hours
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:43.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,我开始理解它了\N{\fs90}and I'm starting to... understand it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.83,0:12:46.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,我开始习惯它了\N{\fs90}I'm starting to get used to it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.19,0:12:49.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,我开始信任它了\N{\fs90}I'm starting to trust it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:52.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,我开始理解\N{\fs90}Now I'm starting to understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:55.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,为什么火神能在\N{\fs90}why the Vulcan can go round the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.11,0:12:59.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,意大利南部Nardo赛道\N{\fs90}Nardo handling circuit in southern Italy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:03.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,比迈凯伦P1还快9秒\N{\fs90}nine seconds faster than the McLaren P1
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.21,0:13:05.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,9秒啊\N{\fs90}Nine seconds
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.98,0:13:07.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,按赛车的标准\N{\fs90}in car time
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.60,0:13:09.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,那就是一年啊\N{\fs90}that's a year!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:16.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,你在低速弯里\N{\fs90}You get phenomenal mechanical grip
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.62,0:13:18.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,有用不尽的抓地力\N{\fs90}in the low-speed corners
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.18,0:13:20.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,在不直道上\N{\fs90}and then, on the Isn't Straight
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.38,0:13:22.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,多亏这出色的空动设计\N{\fs90}thanks to its aerodynamics
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.72,0:13:24.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,又有1.5吨的下压力\N{\fs90}you've got a ton-and-a-half of downforce
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.94,0:13:32.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,然后 还有发动机的动力\N{\fs90}Then you have the power from the engine
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.68,0:13:34.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,感觉\N{\fs90}which feels, well
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.24,0:13:36.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,很老派\N{\fs90}old-fashioned
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.48,0:13:37.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,很彻底\N{\fs90}Proper
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:40.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,我很惊讶它居然没有化油器\N{\fs90}I'm surprised it doesn't have carburettors
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.08,0:13:45.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,我真的好爱它\N{\fs90}I love this thing very much
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.59,0:13:51.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,而我最爱的是\N{\fs90}And what I love most of all
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.38,0:13:53.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,这不是一项实验计划\N{\fs90}is that it's not a test bed
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.46,0:13:57.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,它不是今后汽车发展的范例\N{\fs90}It's not an example of what cars will be like in the future
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.68,0:14:01.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,而是为了颂扬昔日汽车的余晖\N{\fs90}It's a celebration of what they were like in the past
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:04.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,它\N{\fs90}What it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:07.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,就是老式摇滚乐\N{\fs90}is old time rock'n'roll
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:15.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,谢谢 谢谢\N{\fs90}Thank you, thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:17.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,非常感谢\N{\fs90}Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.05,0:14:22.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,-所以 -什么\N{\fs90}-So... -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.18,0:14:23.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,我猜你很喜欢这车\N{\fs90}I get the impression you quite liked the car
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.99,0:14:24.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,超乎想象\N{\fs90}Oh, it's unbelievable
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.83,0:14:26.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,我最喜欢的是\N{\fs90}What I loved most of all is they've made it out of bits
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.29,0:14:29.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,它是由工厂里既有的零件拼凑出来的\N{\fs90}that they already had lying around in the factory
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.96,0:14:32.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,就像你从南非回到家\N{\fs90}It's like you going home after your tripto South Africa
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.06,0:14:33.19,字幕,,0,0,0,,打开冰箱\N{\fs90}opening the fridge
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.19,0:14:34.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,用里面剩下的东西\N{\fs90}and using what's there
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:37.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,做了个无比美味的牧羊人馅饼\N{\fs90}to make a delicious shepherd's pie
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.19,0:14:39.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,就用串味的牛奶和一片老芝士\N{\fs90}What, some stale milk and an old piece of cheese?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:43.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,-它要价多少 180万镑 -没错\N{\fs90}-And it costs £1.8 million? -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.33,0:14:45.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,换算成兰特是多少\N{\fs90}How much is that, Jeremy, in rand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.33,0:14:47.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,十亿三千一百万\N{\fs90}Ten hundred and 30 million and a million
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.30,0:14:53.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,它百公里加速多少 2.9秒\N{\fs90}6But for that it does 0-60 in 2.9 seconds?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.32,0:14:57.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,几乎和大牛 卡特汉姆R600\N{\fs90}So it's nearly as fast as an Aventador or a Caterham R600
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.26,0:14:58.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,艾瑞欧原子V8一样\N{\fs90}or an Ariel Atom V8
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:15:01.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,但要贵太多了啊\N{\fs90}but much more expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.49,0:15:02.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,还不能上路\N{\fs90}And not road legal
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.47,0:15:06.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,谢谢你打压我的激情\N{\fs90}Yes. Thank you very much for relieving yourself all over my enthusiasm
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.64,0:15:07.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,不客气\N{\fs90}You're welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:09.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是辆非常棒的车\N{\fs90}It is a brilliant, brilliant car
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:11.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在只剩一个问题\N{\fs90}And only one question now remains
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.90,0:15:14.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,它在我们赛道上能跑多快\N{\fs90}How fast will it go round our track
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.54,0:15:18.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,开它的男人觉得英伦范\N{\fs90}in the hands of a man who thinks that everything British
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.20,0:15:20.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,基本上就是我党\N{\fs90}is basically communist?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:22.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,他来了\N{\fs90}Here he is
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:24.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,有点困惑\N{\fs90}Looking a bit confused
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.91,0:15:29.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,好 我们看看这堆螺栓有什么能耐\N{\fs90}All right, folks, let's see what this bag of bolts will do
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.08,0:15:31.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,他出发了\N{\fs90}And he's off
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:34.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,立刻就上了不直道\N{\fs90}and immediately on to the Isn't Straight
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.97,0:15:36.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,进入第一弯\N{\fs90}First corner coming up
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.28,0:15:40.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,全油门过弯 胆子很大\N{\fs90}And he's flat through there. That is ballsy
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.49,0:15:43.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,降档进入不直道的\N{\fs90}Changing down, though, for the second corner
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.44,0:15:44.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,第二个弯\N{\fs90}on the Isn't Straight
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:46.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在动力全开\N{\fs90}but now he can use full power
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.08,0:15:48.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,才800匹\N{\fs90}800 brake horsepower?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.39,0:15:49.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,你开玩笑\N{\fs90}Are you kiddin' me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.66,0:15:55.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,留你名弯前大力刹车\N{\fs90}Now, hard on the brakes for Your Name Here
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:57.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,他肯定会被这车感动\N{\fs90}He has got to be impressed with this
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.88,0:15:59.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,大概五万美金\N{\fs90}For about $50,000
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.42,0:16:02.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,就能把我的老卡车改纳斯卡风\N{\fs90}I could get one of my old trucks NASCAR style
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:05.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,也有800匹了啊\N{\fs90}It's got 800 brake horsepower
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.28,0:16:07.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,能去猎鹿\N{\fs90}Go deer hunting
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.88,0:16:10.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,后面还能放几头鹿\N{\fs90}you got room for a couple deer in the back
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:13.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,这车你怎么放鹿\N{\fs90}I don't think you can put no deer in this thing
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.00,0:16:15.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,这里有够多鹿给你撞了\N{\fs90}Plenty of deer to run over, though
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.13,0:16:17.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,回到不直道\N{\fs90}back on the Isn't Straight
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.36,0:16:19.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,007开这个\N{\fs90}James Bond drives one of these
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.92,0:16:23.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,卧槽 范迪塞尔会怼得他菊开肉绽啊\N{\fs90}Shit. Vin Diesel would whip his ass
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.22,0:16:26.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,他肯定会 降到1档\N{\fs90}Yes, I'm sure he would, but down into first
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.74,0:16:29.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,我不懂这货啊\N{\fs90}I don't know about this thing
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.48,0:16:32.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,我说这货像个红头发养子\N{\fs90}It's like a red-headed stepchild I'm talkin'
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.29,0:16:34.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,还丑出翔\N{\fs90}Be damn ugly
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.98,0:16:38.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,不太确定他过外婆家弯时有没有很专心\N{\fs90}Not sure he's fully concentrating past Old Lady's House
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.40,0:16:42.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,地板油通过颠簸路段来到变电箱弯\N{\fs90}But he is flat out towards Substation. It is bumpy here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.07,0:16:45.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,弯心是新柏油 尾巴会不安份吗\N{\fs90}And there's new Tarmac on the apex. Will it kick the tail out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:47.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,果然 但问题不大\N{\fs90}Yes, it does indeed. He's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:49.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,到绵羊坡 今天没羊\N{\fs90}Into Field of Sheep. No sheep today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.98,0:16:52.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,冲过终点\N{\fs90}And he's across the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.58,0:16:56.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,赛道真棒啊\N{\fs90}Hell of a track, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.40,0:16:59.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,-真不错 -车真大\N{\fs90}-It is a hell of a track. -Big car.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:17:02.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,不管怎样 我们来看看圈速榜\N{\fs90}Anyway, we must now bring up the lap board
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,0:17:06.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,看看老美开火神的结果如何\N{\fs90}and find out how fast the American got round in the Vulcan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.06,0:17:07.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,让我们瞧瞧\N{\fs90}Let's have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:10.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,很快啊\N{\fs90}Ooh, it's quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:19.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,你瞧 老派摇滚乐\N{\fs90}There you go, see? Old time rock'n'roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:23.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,老派摇滚乐击败了说唱 电子\N{\fs90}Old time rock'n'roll has beaten rap and techno.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:25.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,还有R&B\N{\fs90}And R and B.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.79,0:17:27.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,荣登榜首\N{\fs90}And is now at the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.36,0:17:28.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,非常棒 好样的\N{\fs90}Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:29.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,干得漂亮 谢谢你\N{\fs90}Well done, and thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:30.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在我们得继续了\N{\fs90}Now we must move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.42,0:17:35.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为我们现在该去唠嗑街散散步了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.35,0:17:43.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,好 接着说阿斯顿马丁\N{\fs90}Right, sticking with Aston Martin
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.28,0:17:45.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们和红牛车队一起\N{\fs90}they've teamed up with Red Bull Racing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.48,0:17:47.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,合作打造了这个\N{\fs90} to create this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.28,0:17:49.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,它叫做001\N{\fs90}It's called the 001.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.80,0:17:52.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,它搭载一台V12 没有涡轮\N{\fs90}It has a V12, no turbos
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.24,0:17:54.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,没有那种混动魔法\N{\fs90}none of that sort of hybrid witchcraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.91,0:17:58.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,但它能输出900马力\N{\fs90}Yet it produces 900 horsepower
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.00,0:18:02.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,而这车只重900千克\N{\fs90}in a car that only weighs 900 kilos.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:04.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,惊人啊\N{\fs90}Staggering.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.12,0:18:06.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,岂止惊人啊 那简直就是神级数据\N{\fs90}Well, more than staggering, that is a magic figure,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.63,0:18:09.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为那意味着它的功重比是1:1\N{\fs90}cos that means it has one horsepower per kilogram.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:11.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,而没有车能接近这个数据\N{\fs90}And no other car gets close to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.16,0:18:14.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,还差得远 火神几乎只有它的一半\N{\fs90}Not remotely. The Vulcan's barely half that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.52,0:18:15.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,这很惊人\N{\fs90}It's staggering.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.68,0:18:17.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,这车唯一的问题\N{\fs90}The only problem
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:18.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,你只用看着它就知道了\N{\fs90}I have with this... and you just have to look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:20.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们还有另一个角度的照片\N{\fs90}Another angle we've got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.29,0:18:21.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,看那儿\N{\fs90}Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:24.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,你就知道这车的重点会是空气动力\N{\fs90}You know that car is gonna be all about aerodynamics
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.42,0:18:26.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,特别是下压力\N{\fs90}and particularly downforce.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:28.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,而我讨厌下压力\N{\fs90}And I hate downforce.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:30.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,你啥意思啊 你讨厌下压力?\N{\fs90}What do you mean, you hate downforce?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.43,0:18:31.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为他们告诉你说\N{\fs90}Because they tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.84,0:18:34.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,你能以160公里时速通过90度的弯\N{\fs90}you can go round a 90-degree bend at 100mph
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.99,0:18:37.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为空气对车身的下压力\N{\fs90}because of the weight of the air pressing down on the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.32,0:18:39.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,像是有一头隐形的大象在上面\N{\fs90}It's like having an invisible elephant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.56,0:18:42.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,那这头大象摔下来了咋办\N{\fs90}What if the elephant falls off?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:44.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,又不是真有一头大象\N{\fs90}It's not a real elephant!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.92,0:18:46.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,-不可能摔下来 -你又看不见\N{\fs90}-It can't fall off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:48.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,但你怎么能相信你看不见的东西\N{\fs90}But how can you trust something you don't see?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:49.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,等下 我同意他\N{\fs90}Wait. No, I'm with him
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.61,0:18:52.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,万一你突然开进真空里了怎么办\N{\fs90}because what if you drove through a sudden vacuum?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.08,0:18:54.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,但那也不可能发生啊 不是么\N{\fs90}Well, that's not gonna happen either, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.61,0:18:55.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德 听着\N{\fs90}Hammond, listen. There has to be a speed
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.70,0:18:59.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,这种依靠主动下压力的车 必然在某个速度\N{\fs90}in a car with active downforce, like that one,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.15,0:19:02.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,当你过弯时 速度快到轮胎无法承受\N{\fs90}where you go round a corner too fast for the tyres,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:03.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,快到抓地力无法支持\N{\fs90}too fast for the mechanical grip,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.60,0:19:06.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,但又没快到下压力能起作用\N{\fs90}but not fast enough for the downforce to be working.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.78,0:19:08.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以你就得对警察说\N{\fs90}So you'd have to say to the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.23,0:19:11.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,"我是因为开得不够快才撞车的"\N{\fs90}"I crashed because I wasn't going fast enough."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.52,0:19:12.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,-说真的 -是有可能\N{\fs90}It's true. -Potentially.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.95,0:19:14.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,其实还有一点\N{\fs90}There's another point, actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.08,0:19:16.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为操控要视天气情况而定 是吧\N{\fs90}the handling is gonna depend on the weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.08,0:19:18.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,如果天气很炎热\N{\fs90}If it's a really hot day
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.18,0:19:19.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,那空气就会更稀薄\N{\fs90}the air will be thinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.52,0:19:20.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,不对 是更稠密\N{\fs90}No, thicker.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.44,0:19:22.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 热天空气更稀薄\N{\fs90}No, it's thinner on a hot day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:23.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,看 我已经搞混了\N{\fs90}See, I'd be messed up already cos
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.76,0:19:24.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,我就会弄错\N{\fs90}I'd have the wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.75,0:19:26.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,这就是重点啊 天气很炎热\N{\fs90}That's the point. You got a really hot day,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.45,0:19:27.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,你就不想开一辆\N{\fs90}and you don't really want to be driving a car
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.89,0:19:29.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,能不能过弯\N{\fs90}where whether or not you get round a corner
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.94,0:19:31.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,取决于有没有太阳的车\N{\fs90}depends on whether or not the sun's out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.76,0:19:35.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以你想让天气预报里加上过弯速度\N{\fs90}So you now want weather forecasts to include cornering speeds?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.20,0:19:37.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,不只是天气啊 还有海拔\N{\fs90}It's not just weather. Altitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:41.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,在荷兰 零海拔 能开着那车以160的时速过弯\N{\fs90}You could drive that car round a corner at 100mph in Holland, sea level,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.66,0:19:44.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,但这儿呢 海拔1829米\N{\fs90}but, what are we here, 6,000 feet up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.06,0:19:45.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,这儿海拔1829米\N{\fs90}6,000 feet up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:47.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,你能以5公里时速过弯就不错了\N{\fs90}You'd barely be able to get round at three mph.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.67,0:19:50.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,你会撞树上 或者一头真的大象上\N{\fs90}You'd crash it into a tree, or a visible elephant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:51.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,它们确实是真的\N{\fs90}They are real.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.39,0:19:53.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,没错啊 我就是 说实话\N{\fs90}Exactly. I just... Honestly
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.72,0:19:55.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,下压力\N{\fs90}downforce...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.80,0:19:58.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢相信看不见的东西\N{\fs90}I don't like having to trust something you can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.24,0:19:59.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,就像朝鲜一样\N{\fs90}It's like North Korea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.70,0:20:03.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,或者像避孕药\N{\fs90}Or the contraceptive pill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:08.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,说得有点儿多\N{\fs90}That was an overshare.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.30,0:20:12.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,其实还有一辆我想让你们注意的超跑\N{\fs90}There's actually another hyper car I want to draw your attention to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.61,0:20:14.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,威龙的替任者\N{\fs90}Replacement for the Veyron.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:16.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,那是布加迪 Chiron\N{\fs90}That is the Bugatti Chiron.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.68,0:20:20.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,它搭载了一台8升W16四涡轮发动机\N{\fs90}It's got a quad turbo 8-litre W16 engine,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.48,0:20:24.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,每分钟能吸入60000升空气\N{\fs90}which every minute inhales 13,000 gallons of air.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.44,0:20:26.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,-想象下 -难以置信\N{\fs90}-Just imagine -It's unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.53,0:20:28.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,1500马力\N{\fs90}1,500 horsepower.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:32.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,而最高时速被限制在420公里\N{\fs90}And the top speed is limited to 261 mph.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.82,0:20:35.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们说能达到463公里\N{\fs90}They say it would do 288
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.14,0:20:37.80,字幕,,0,0,0,, 但在公路上是不负责任的\N{\fs90}but that would be irresponsible on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.74,0:20:41.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,为了音质更好 它音响里还有钻石\N{\fs90}It's got diamonds in the speakers for better sound quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:42.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,它当然有咯\N{\fs90}Of course it has, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:43.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,这点你会喜欢的\N{\fs90}Oh, you'll like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.42,0:20:48.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,在极速时 每个轮胎上的力达3800G\N{\fs90}At top speed, the force on each tyre is 3800G.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.04,0:20:51.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,9G就能让人丧生\N{\fs90}A man dies at 9G.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.22,0:20:53.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,如果你极速驾驶Chrion的话\N{\fs90}If you drive the Chiron flat out
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.03,0:20:56.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,它将在9分钟内耗尽油箱里的油\N{\fs90}it'll drain its tank in nine minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.91,0:20:58.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,9分钟\N{\fs90}Nine minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.41,0:21:01.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,等一下 420公里时速开9分钟\N{\fs90}Hang on a minute. 261mph at nine minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.84,0:21:05.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,那就是说你每开63公里就得加油\N{\fs90}That means you'd have to fill up with fuel every 39 miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.44,0:21:06.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,实际上还不到63公里\N{\fs90}Well, less
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.65,0:21:08.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为不能开到干 你得尽早寻找加油站\N{\fs90}- you can't drive until you run out, you'd have to look for a petrol station.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.92,0:21:12.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,是的 詹姆斯 这车太不实用了 是吧\N{\fs90}Yes, James, it really isn't a practical car, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.11,0:21:14.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,但我要给你们说下最厉害的数据\N{\fs90}Gonna give you the most amazing stat, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.68,0:21:15.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,和这车本身没关系\N{\fs90}It's about the people who are buying this car.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.75,0:21:17.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,而是和要买这车的人有关系\N{\fs90}It's about the people who are buying this car.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.37,0:21:19.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们目前为止接到了200个订单\N{\fs90}They've got 200 orders so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.10,0:21:21.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,而平均下来 每个预订了一辆的人\N{\fs90}And the average person who's ordered one
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.14,0:21:24.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,都已经拥有了64辆车\N{\fs90}already has 64 cars
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.06,0:21:25.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,3架直升机\N{\fs90}three helicopters
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.36,0:21:27.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,3架飞机和1辆游艇\N{\fs90}three jets and one yacht
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.28,0:21:29.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,是说祖玛么\N{\fs90}Zuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.06,0:21:37.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,我猜他已经买了一辆了\N{\fs90}I reckon he's got one already.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.90,0:21:41.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,没说 他可没说过\N{\fs90}Didn't say that. He didn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.34,0:21:42.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们能继续么\N{\fs90}Shall we move it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.32,0:21:47.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,在南非 每天会发生35起劫车案件\N{\fs90}In South Africa, there are 35 carjackings every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.27,0:21:50.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,-每天? -每天\N{\fs90}Every day? -Every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.17,0:21:51.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,我不得不说\N{\fs90}I've got to say
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.42,0:21:53.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,干得漂亮 这数目很惊人啊\N{\fs90}well done, that's an amazing figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.18,0:21:56.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,难以置信 你们哪有时间来这儿啊\N{\fs90}I can't believe it. How have you got time to come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:21:58.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,你们有活儿要干吧\N{\fs90}Cos you've got stuff to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.68,0:22:01.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们都是开别人的车来的\N{\fs90}They've all come here in someone else's car.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.02,0:22:02.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦 所以你们是已经抢完了\N{\fs90}So you've already done it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.28,0:22:02.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,我懂了\N{\fs90}I Understing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.94,0:22:04.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,但他们没意识到 回去只能靠走的了\N{\fs90}But what they don't realise is they're all walking home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.62,0:22:05.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs90}Anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.32,0:22:06.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,总之\N{\fs90}emmm
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.33,0:22:07.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,我做了点儿调查\N{\fs90}I've done a bit of research.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.34,0:22:09.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,被劫的最多的车\N{\fs90}The most commonly jacked cars
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.97,0:22:11.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,被劫的车\N{\fs90}carjacked cars
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.49,0:22:15.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,是大众Polo 丰田海狮 丰田海拉克斯\N{\fs90}are the VW Polo, the Toyota Hiace and the Toyota Hilux.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.45,0:22:17.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,但它们是在南非卖得最好的车\N{\fs90}But they're the best-selling cars in South Africa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.26,0:22:20.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,没错 大众Polo是南非的销量冠军\N{\fs90}Exactly. The VW Polo is the best-selling car in South Africa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.04,0:22:21.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,那你们为啥要买一辆\N{\fs90}So why would you buy a car
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.62,0:22:24.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,会增加你被爆头和被偷的几率的车\N{\fs90}which increases your chance of being shot in the head and your car being stolen?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.07,0:22:29.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,你们为啥不买一辆没人想偷的车\N{\fs90}Why not buy a car that nobody would want to steal?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.38,0:22:31.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,对啊 如果我住这 我就不会买那些\N{\fs90}No, cos if I lived here
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.22,0:22:33.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,我会买辆米色的沃尔沃旅行车\N{\fs90}I'd get something like a beige Volvo Estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.89,0:22:35.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,那明明就是你想要的车\N{\fs90}That's just a car you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.89,0:22:39.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,你在拿这事当借口 买你的梦想之车\N{\fs90}You're using it as an excuse to get your dream car.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.64,0:22:41.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,听着 哈蒙德\N{\fs90}Look, Hammond
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.02,0:22:43.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,我以前给你解释过\N{\fs90}I've explained it to you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.17,0:22:46.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,买一辆沃尔沃旅行车 有点儿像是去看牙医\N{\fs90}Having a Volvo Estate is a bit like needing to go to the dentist.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.86,0:22:48.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是注定的事 早晚得解决\N{\fs90}It's gonna happen. Get it over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.30,0:22:49.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,买就是了\N{\fs90}Just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.02,0:22:51.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,我不想把它解决了\N{\fs90}I don't want to get it over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.80,0:22:53.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为那像是去对牙医说\N{\fs90}That's like going to the dentist and saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.34,0:22:54.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,"把我的牙全拔了"\N{\fs90}"Take all my teeth out"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.35,0:22:55.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,"反正它们都会掉光"\N{\fs90}"cos they're gonna fall out."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.14,0:22:55.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,或者是去理发店说\N{\fs90}At the barber's
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.94,0:22:58.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,"拔光 反正它们都会掉完的"\N{\fs90}"Just pull it all out, it'll fall out anyway."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.14,0:22:59.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,或者去看医生\N{\fs90}The doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.01,0:23:02.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,"你能让我尿失禁吗 反正都得尿的"\N{\fs90}"Stop me being able to retain my urine. It's gonna happen, too."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.65,0:23:04.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,我要把自己活埋了\N{\fs90}I'm gonna bury myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.14,0:23:05.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,然后一次性解决所有问题\N{\fs90}and get it all over with once and for all
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.96,0:23:07.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,说真的 他说得有道理\N{\fs90}He has got a point, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.70,0:23:10.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,在必须买沃尔沃之前 先好好享受吧\N{\fs90}Let's enjoy it before we have to have the Volvo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.52,0:23:14.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,但你们为啥要买会被抢劫的车啊\N{\fs90}But why do you all buy cars that you're going to get carjacked in?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.36,0:23:16.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,有人开大众Polo么\N{\fs90}Has anyone got a Volkswagen Polo here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.72,0:23:18.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,你有\N{\fs90}You have?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.78,0:23:20.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,那车你自己买的吗\N{\fs90}Did you buy that for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.07,0:23:22.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,你爸给你买的\N{\fs90}My dad bought it for me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.95,0:23:25.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,哇喔 这个礼物好啊\N{\fs90}Oh, nice gift!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.53,0:23:28.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是有多疯啊\N{\fs90}What sort of madness is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.04,0:23:30.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,那有人开丰田海拉克斯吗\N{\fs90}Has anyone got a Toyota Hilux?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.07,0:23:33.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,有哈 这是疯了\N{\fs90}Yeah. This is insanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.00,0:23:34.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,是你的么\N{\fs90}Is it yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.48,0:23:38.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,今早上出门你开的啥\N{\fs90}What did you start out with this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.10,0:23:40.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,难以置信啊\N{\fs90}It's unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.02,0:23:42.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,总之 继续往下说\N{\fs90}Anyway, listen, we gotta move it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.16,0:23:43.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为 在南非这儿\N{\fs90}Because, here in South Africa,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.78,0:23:46.59,字幕,,0,0,0,,人们有个防止盗车的办法很有意思\N{\fs90}people have an interesting approach to preventing car theft.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.59,0:23:48.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,这儿有张图 是一个人的办法\N{\fs90}Got a picture here of one man's solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.44,0:23:50.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,那是条巨蟒\N{\fs90}That's a python.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.30,0:23:52.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,没错 这样肯定有用\N{\fs90}Now there's no question it's gonna work
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.66,0:23:54.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,仪表盘上有那玩意儿的车\N{\fs90}I would not steal a car
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.32,0:23:55.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,我是不会去偷的\N{\fs90}that had that on the dashboard
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.76,0:23:58.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,然而 一条巨蟒不像防盗报警器\N{\fs90}However, a python's not like a burglar alarm
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.23,0:23:59.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,你不能把它关了\N{\fs90}You can't turn it off
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.52,0:24:00.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,那当你上车时\N{\fs90}When you come back to your car
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.91,0:24:02.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,该怎么给那条蛇解释\N{\fs90}how do you say to the snake
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.11,0:24:04.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,"这是我的车 别勒死我"\N{\fs90}"It's my car, don't strangle me."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.51,0:24:05.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,你没办法\N{\fs90}You can't
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.62,0:24:07.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,我很确定你是没法训练巨蟒的 是吧\N{\fs90}I'm pretty sure you can't train a python, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.74,0:24:10.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,当然不能 所以你从没看到过牧羊蛇\N{\fs90}You can't. That's why you never see sheep snakes
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.00,0:24:11.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,或者帮助盲人的导盲蛇\N{\fs90}or guide snakes for the blind
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.91,0:24:13.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,这从未有过\N{\fs90}It'll never happen
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.91,0:24:15.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,但我得说 我得说\N{\fs90}I have to say
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.72,0:24:18.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,在英国我们有个更蠢的办法\N{\fs90}in England, we've got an even more stupid solution
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.44,0:24:21.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,有人想出了一个叫做 单车地雷 的点子\N{\fs90}This chap's come up with an idea called "Bike Mine"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.26,0:24:24.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,这儿有个他解释这办法的视频\N{\fs90}I've got a video of him here explaining how it works
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.81,0:24:27.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,它能快速地装上 来保护几乎任何个人财产\N{\fs90}It can be attached quickly to protect almost any personal possession
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.96,0:24:30.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,不管是放在室外 或是车库里 棚子里的\N{\fs90}you store outside or in a garage or shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.60,0:24:33.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,它坚固的钢结构被一层橡胶包裹着\N{\fs90}Its robust steel construction is covered in a rubber skin
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.70,0:24:35.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,以保护你的财产\N{\fs90}to protect your property.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.23,0:24:36.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,单车地雷 很安全\N{\fs90}Bike Mine is safe
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.62,0:24:39.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为它上面的雷管是独立的\N{\fs90}because the detonators are self-contained...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.26,0:24:41.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,并且是可以合法拥有和使用的\N{\fs90}as well as legal to own and use.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.54,0:24:42.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,单车地雷 很可靠\N{\fs90}Bike Mine is reliable
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.90,0:24:44.47,字幕,,0,0,0,, 因为没有电池也就不会耗电\N{\fs90}because there are no batteries to run down
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.47,0:24:46.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且只有一个活动部分\N{\fs90}and only one moving part
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.69,0:24:54.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,这绝对管用\N{\fs90}It's not gonna work.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.12,0:24:55.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,我不能理解的是\N{\fs90}What I can't understand is
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.92,0:24:57.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,他说的是它也能用来保护\N{\fs90}he said it can also protect
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.92,0:25:00.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,你所拥有的任何其它个人财产\N{\fs90}any other personal property you may have
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.47,0:25:02.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,啥 比如明朝的花瓶\N{\fs90}What, like a Ming vase?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.28,0:25:06.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,你担心你的孩子被绑架吗\N{\fs90}"Are you worried about your child being kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.02,0:25:08.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,只需要把炸弹挂在他们脖子上\N{\fs90}Simply hang this bomb round their neck
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.72,0:25:12.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,下面来到约旦 奇怪吧\N{\fs90}So, moving on, to Jordan, weirdly
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.36,0:25:15.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,当地政府刚建了座实训基地\N{\fs90}where the government has just built a mock town
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.27,0:25:17.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,世界各地的特种部队\N{\fs90}so that special forces from all over the world
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.83,0:25:19.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,都可以来这里\N{\fs90}can turn up and have a competition
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.83,0:25:22.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,一决高低\N{\fs90}to see which one is best
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.63,0:25:23.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,没错 而今年\N{\fs90}Yes, and this year
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.92,0:25:27.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,掌管大权的胖子威尔曼\N{\fs90}Mr Wilman who is the Fat Man who controls our lives
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.36,0:25:30.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,决定让我们也去参加一下\N{\fs90}decided that us three should go and take part
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.05,0:25:32.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,显然其中会有大量枪战\N{\fs90}Obviously there'd be a lot of shooting
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.05,0:25:34.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,跑动以及翻爬\N{\fs90}running about and doing somersaults
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.05,0:25:36.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们没一样擅长的\N{\fs90}None of which we'd be any good at
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.05,0:25:39.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,但英国特种航空队 世界第一支特种部队\N{\fs90}No, but, the SAS, the world's first special forces unit
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.67,0:25:41.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,创立要义就在于迅速\N{\fs90}was created to be fast
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.96,0:25:43.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,迅速切入战场迅速撤离\N{\fs90}to get into the battle quickly and then get out again
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.98,0:25:47.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,高速驾驶也是重头戏之一\N{\fs90}So there would also be a lot of high-speed driving
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.10,0:25:48.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,额 对我明白\N{\fs90}Yes, I know
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.61,0:25:50.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,他确实是个问题 我们要想办法\N{\fs90}That is a bit of a problem. We'll gloss over that
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.05,0:25:55.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,于是我们前往战场 以下是详细情况\N{\fs90}Anyway, we were sent out there and this is what happened
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.65,0:26:12.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,就是这里\N{\fs90}This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.72,0:26:16.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,坐落于安曼深处的特训基地\N{\fs90}The special forces training base deep inside Amman.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.72,0:26:19.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,是说城市 没别的意思\N{\fs90}The city, obviously, not... not...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.65,0:26:20.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,总之 一支特种小队将会\N{\fs90}Anyway a squad of special forces soldiers
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.92,0:26:26.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,展示我们接下来要做的事\N{\fs90}arriving now to demonstrate what we'd have to do later
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.50,0:26:30.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,首先从黑鹰直升机上索降\N{\fs90}They exfoliated from a Black Hawk helicopter on ropes
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.47,0:26:34.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,然后攻入一栋恐怖分子控制的建筑\N{\fs90}and then fought their way through a terrorist-infested building
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.81,0:26:43.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,随后偷一部车\N{\fs90}Their next task was to steal a car
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.27,0:26:46.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,前往被劫持的航班\N{\fs90}which they used to reach a hijacked airliner
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.01,0:26:52.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,攻进客舱 杀光坏蛋\N{\fs90}Here they stormed the cabin, killed the bad guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.07,0:26:57.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,营救目标人物\N{\fs90}and rescued a VIP
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.54,0:27:03.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,接下来 高速追车 行进中枪战\N{\fs90}There was then a high-speed car chase and a running gun battle
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.58,0:27:05.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,将被救人质护送至\N{\fs90}as they escorted the rescued hostage
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.54,0:27:08.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,就近的大使馆安全区域\N{\fs90}to the safety of a nearby embassy
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.70,0:27:16.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,真让人印象深刻啊\N{\fs90}That was quite impressive
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.18,0:27:18.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们用的不像是实弹\N{\fs90}Well, it's not like they were using real bullets
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.81,0:27:21.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 是实弹 -明明不是 -是的\N{\fs90}-Yes, they were -They were not -They were!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.43,0:27:23.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,你是说 在这种\N{\fs90}Are you saying that on this
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.25,0:27:25.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,老实说就是 训练场中\N{\fs90}let's be honest, training ground
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.21,0:27:29.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,人们可以用装了实弹的枪打来打去\N{\fs90}people are allowed to run around with real bullets in these guns?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.41,0:27:30.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,-是啊 -胡说\N{\fs90}-Yes -Rubbish.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.34,0:27:36.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,看吧 实弹\N{\fs90}And there you are. Real bullets
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.74,0:27:39.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,我简直是朝自己射了\N{\fs90}And I managed to shoot myself
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.61,0:27:41.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,是吗 你怎么弄的\N{\fs90}-Oh, yeah -How did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.98,0:27:45.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为这突击步枪 弹壳从这方向出来\N{\fs90}Well, because, on an assault rifle, the bullets come out this side
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.58,0:27:48.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,我习惯左手持枪 弹壳直接打我手臂上了\N{\fs90}and I'm a left-handed shot, so they just go up my arm, the casings
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.87,0:27:50.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,你打枪真垃圾\N{\fs90}You're gonna be rubbish at this
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.34,0:27:53.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,那我就没法用突击步枪了\N{\fs90}Well, I'm not going to be able to use an assault rifle
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.07,0:27:55.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,我都没法攻进那架飞机\N{\fs90}I'm not gonna be able to storm that airliner
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.98,0:27:57.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,我都没法从直升机上下来\N{\fs90}I'm not gonna be able to get out of the helicopter
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.47,0:28:03.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,正担心事情可能不会很顺利\N{\fs90}Fearing that things may not go well
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.18,0:28:04.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们被通知去做准备\N{\fs90}we were told to go and get ready
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.98,0:28:08.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,没想到连这都困难重重\N{\fs90}And even that was fraught with difficulty
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.96,0:28:13.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,你为什么穿成白色\N{\fs90}Why are you wearing white?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.12,0:28:14.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,雪地迷彩啊\N{\fs90}Snow camouflage
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.45,0:28:18.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,约旦就从没下过雪\N{\fs90}It has never, ever snowed in Jordan
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.41,0:28:20.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,我之前不知道约旦在哪\N{\fs90}I didn't know where Jordan was
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.50,0:28:22.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,你会很显眼\N{\fs90}You're gonna be quite visible
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.27,0:28:28.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,这时 我们收到老大发来的任务说明\N{\fs90}At this point, we received details of our mission from our boss
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.25,0:28:29.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,威尔曼先生\N{\fs90}Mr Wilman
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.25,0:28:32.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,只要其中一人死亡\N{\fs90}Each time one of you is killed
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.25,0:28:34.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,你们全部都要重新开始\N{\fs90}you all have to begin again
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.67,0:28:37.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,像是汤姆克鲁斯电影啊\N{\fs90}So it's like that Tom Cruise movie
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.18,0:28:39.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,花心情圣吗\N{\fs90}What, Cocktail?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.92,0:28:42.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,不是花心情圣 也不是雨人\N{\fs90}No, not Cocktail. Or Rain Man
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.96,0:28:44.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,这永远也完不成啊\N{\fs90}This is gonna take forever
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.03,0:28:56.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,很快我们便乘直升机\N{\fs90}Nevertheless, we were soon in the helicopter
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.18,0:28:59.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,前往这次重要营救任务的起点\N{\fs90}on our way to the start of this important rescue mission
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.41,0:29:03.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们先缕清楚\N{\fs90}Let's just get this straight
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.12,0:29:05.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们到达建筑上空时\N{\fs90}When we get over the building
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.61,0:29:07.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,从舱门跳出去\N{\fs90}we leap out of the door
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.61,0:29:09.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,抓住绳索然后滑下去吗\N{\fs90}and grab the rope and slide down it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.61,0:29:11.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,差不多是这样 是这么玩的\N{\fs90}Pretty much, yeah, that's it. That's how it goes
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.61,0:29:13.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,你可以带头\N{\fs90}You could be leader
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.10,0:29:17.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,冲出去 做个示范 我们会跟着的\N{\fs90}Get out there, show us how it's done, we will follow
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.63,0:29:18.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,我不想去\N{\fs90}I don't want to
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.96,0:29:22.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,我这辈子从来没爬过绳子\N{\fs90}I've never climbed a rope or gone down one in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.30,0:29:23.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,多好的机会 该抓住啊\N{\fs90}Well, what a time. Get on with it
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.52,0:29:24.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,你为什么不先去\N{\fs90}Why don't you go first?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.74,0:29:27.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,我做不到 我恐高\N{\fs90}I can't do that. I'm scared of heights
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.85,0:29:29.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,以身作则吧\N{\fs90}Lead by example
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.47,0:29:32.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,-鼓舞下你的团队 -说得好\N{\fs90}-Be an inspiration to your men. -Yeah, exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.36,0:29:34.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,高度有多少\N{\fs90}How high will it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.81,0:29:38.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,有10米 差不多吧\N{\fs90}30 feet?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.56,0:29:41.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,从10米高度摔下去会怎样\N{\fs90}What happens if you fell 30 feet?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.03,0:29:43.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,还能完整的回家吗\N{\fs90}Would you be going home with a head wand?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.58,0:29:45.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,你还会坐这架飞机回去\N{\fs90}You'd be going home in this helicopter
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.03,0:29:46.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,不过不是坐座位上\N{\fs90}but not in that seat
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.03,0:29:48.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,你会被装在角落的桶里\N{\fs90}You'd be in a bucket in the corner
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.57,0:29:59.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,来吧 大干一场吧\N{\fs90}OK, here it comes. Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.52,0:30:08.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,哇 老天爷 停下\N{\fs90}Whoa! Jesus Christ! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.25,0:30:10.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢 我靠\N{\fs90}Oh, shit
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.76,0:30:12.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,我好害怕\N{\fs90}I'm very scared
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.07,0:30:14.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,老兄 这态度不行\N{\fs90}Mate, that's not the attitude
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.18,0:30:15.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,-冲吧 -我不喜欢这个\N{\fs90}-Go on, then! -Don't like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.54,0:30:17.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,-滑下绳子去 -我不想\N{\fs90}-Go down the rope! -Don't want to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.01,0:30:19.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,-手松一点 -我不想这么做\N{\fs90}-Loosen your hands a bit. -I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.01,0:30:21.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,你想让我挠你肚子吗\N{\fs90}Do you want me to tickle you on your belly?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.01,0:30:23.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,-不想 -那快去做啊\N{\fs90}-No. -Well, go on, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.21,0:30:30.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,-哈蒙德 -怎么了\N{\fs90}-Hammond! -Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.74,0:30:32.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,我裤子掉了\N{\fs90}My trousers have fallen down
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.12,0:30:36.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们 简直是查克 诺里斯啊\N{\fs90}Ladies and gentlemen, Chuck Norris
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.12,0:30:40.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢不 天哪\N{\fs90}Oh, no, no
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.74,0:30:46.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,终于到了 你们此生\N{\fs90}Oh, yes. Have you ever in your whole life seen anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.83,0:30:48.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,有曾见过什么比这\N{\fs90}Oh, yes. Have you ever in your whole life seen anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.27,0:30:49.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\fs90}Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.21,0:30:57.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,事情被我搞的显得有点难
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.74,0:31:00.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,但其实超级简单的\N{\fs90}but actually it's surprisingly easy
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.52,0:31:03.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以这次不如你先上吧\N{\fs90}So, why don't you go first?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.54,0:31:05.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我有个更好的主意 -什么\N{\fs90}-I've got a better idea. -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.85,0:31:07.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,为什么不直接降落直升机\N{\fs90}Why don't we just land the helicopter?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.85,0:31:10.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,好主意 直升机都能落地的\N{\fs90}That is a good idea. Helicopters can land
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.54,0:31:27.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,停住停住 哈蒙德\N{\fs90}Stop, stop, stop. Hammond
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.52,0:31:31.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,这样 你打开门\N{\fs90}Right, listen, you open the door
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.72,0:31:33.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,我丢个震撼弹进去\N{\fs90}and I'll throw this stun grenade in
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.41,0:31:34.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,好主意 倒数三...\N{\fs90}Good idea. In three...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.43,0:31:35.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,-不 等下等下 -怎么了\N{\fs90}No, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.94,0:31:37.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,我不知道怎么用\N{\fs90}I don't know how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.54,0:31:38.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢老天爷啊\N{\fs90}Oh, for God's sake
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.70,0:31:44.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗 哈蒙德\N{\fs90}Right. You ready, Hammond?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.03,0:31:46.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,上啊\N{\fs90}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.32,0:31:49.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,冲啊\N{\fs90}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.76,0:31:55.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,你不是说震撼弹吗\N{\fs90}I thought you said it was a stun grenade?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.47,0:31:56.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,烟幕弹 说错了\N{\fs90}I meant smoke
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.61,0:31:59.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,我啥都看不见\N{\fs90}I can't see a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.98,0:32:01.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,完全瞎了\N{\fs90}Literally nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.85,0:32:05.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,等烟雾消散了 我们开始搜查建筑\N{\fs90}When the smoke finally cleared,we started our sweep
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.47,0:32:08.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,安静\N{\fs90}Ssh. Quiet
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.96,0:32:21.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,这代表有狗 是有狗吗\N{\fs90}Dog. Dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.21,0:32:24.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 我是说门 那有扇门\N{\fs90}No! It means door. There's a door!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.74,0:32:26.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,这有扇门\N{\fs90}There's a door.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.52,0:32:28.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,你以为它是足球吗\N{\fs90}It's not a bloody football, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.87,0:32:31.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,踹开它 用脚平着踹\N{\fs90}Kick it You put your foot flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.34,0:32:34.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,就这么干\N{\fs90}That's how you do it
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.65,0:32:37.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,没人在 空的\N{\fs90}Nobody there It's empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.90,0:32:44.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,没人\N{\fs90}Nobody there
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.38,0:32:49.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,很快 人来了\N{\fs90}Soon, though, they were there
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.72,0:33:00.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们困在房间里了\N{\fs90}We are trapped in this room
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.90,0:33:02.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,为什么不从窗户出去\N{\fs90}Well, why don't we just go out of the window?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.34,0:33:04.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,可以从窗户出去啊\N{\fs90}We could go out of the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.65,0:33:07.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,好像是可以 掩护我们\N{\fs90}Yeah, we could do that. Cover us
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.32,0:33:08.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,好 我掩护你们\N{\fs90}Yeah, I'll cover you
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.50,0:33:13.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,在杰瑞米的火力掩护下\N{\fs90}As Jeremy laid down covering fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.56,0:33:16.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,梅和我从窗户爬了出来\N{\fs90}...May and I climbed out of the window
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.87,0:33:19.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,但随后问题来了\N{\fs90}But then, there was a problem
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.07,0:33:25.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,我卡住了\N{\fs90}I'm stuck
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.12,0:33:26.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,挤出来啊\N{\fs90}Well, push!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.52,0:33:33.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,-怎么了 -恐怖分子进房间了\N{\fs90}-What? -The terrorists are in the room
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.14,0:33:34.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道\N{\fs90}How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.70,0:33:36.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们在搞我\N{\fs90}They're doing things to me
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.78,0:33:44.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,好难受啊\N{\fs90}This is very uncomfortable
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.34,0:33:46.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,可能是你太紧张了\N{\fs90}It's probably cos you're so tense
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.78,0:33:47.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢 詹姆斯\N{\fs90}James!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.67,0:33:49.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,-干嘛 -杀了我\N{\fs90}-What? -Kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.67,0:33:51.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,-打死我吧 -乐意之极\N{\fs90}-Shoot me. -Gladly
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.98,0:33:54.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,麻烦快点\N{\fs90}Please hurry up
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.45,0:33:56.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,全自动模式 额\N{\fs90}Fully automatic?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.38,0:33:57.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,快点动手啊\N{\fs90}Get on with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.76,0:33:59.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,给他个痛快吧 倒数十\N{\fs90}Just give him the lot. In ten...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.43,0:34:00.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,不要倒数十了\N{\fs90}Not ten!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.92,0:34:03.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧 倒数三\N{\fs90}All right, in... three
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.54,0:34:05.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,二 一\N{\fs90}two, one.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.94,0:34:09.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,这都能打偏\N{\fs90}How did you miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.81,0:34:11.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,都说自动步枪开火很不准\N{\fs90}It's true what they say about machine guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.96,0:34:13.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,果然如此啊\N{\fs90}You can't hit a thing with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.38,0:34:15.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,-干嘛 -快杀了我\N{\fs90}-What? -Just kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.56,0:34:17.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们在努力 没那么容易的\N{\fs90}We're trying! It's not that easy
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.72,0:34:19.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,等下 我没子弹了\N{\fs90}Hang on. I'm out
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.01,0:34:21.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,-用铲子拍死我吧 -好吧\N{\fs90}Use the shovel. Hit me with that. -Right
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.01,0:34:23.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,有什么遗言吗\N{\fs90}Do you want to say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.03,0:34:25.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,有 最后一句 我恨你们\N{\fs90}Yes. Final words. I hate you
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.03,0:34:26.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,你知道 我做梦都想这么干\N{\fs90}You know, I've dreamt about exactly this
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.41,0:34:28.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,-快点啊 -接招吧\N{\fs90}-Hurry up! -Incoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.61,0:34:37.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们困在房间里了\N{\fs90}We are trapped in this room
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.03,0:34:38.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,为什么不从窗户出去\N{\fs90}Why don't we go out of the window?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.92,0:34:40.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,我可以从门出去吗\N{\fs90}Do you mind if I go through the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.67,0:34:45.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,这样好多了\N{\fs90}This is better
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.81,0:34:53.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们英勇地消灭了外边所有敌人\N{\fs90}Heroically we fought off all the attackers outside the building
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.65,0:34:58.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,但被一个狙击手盯上了\N{\fs90}But then we were pinned down by a sniper
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.21,0:35:05.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,-詹姆斯 詹姆斯 -什么事\N{\fs90}James. James. -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.02,0:35:07.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,去把那辆雷诺偷来\N{\fs90}Go down there and steal that Renault
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.67,0:35:08.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fs90}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.89,0:35:11.59,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为这是汽车节目 我们要有汽车元素\N{\fs90}Because this is a car show. We need a motoring element.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.59,0:35:12.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,-有道理 -去吧\N{\fs90}Good point. -Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.67,0:35:17.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,你觉得在这颗星球上\N{\fs90}Can you think of anybody on God's green Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.97,0:35:21.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,还有比他更不靠谱的吗\N{\fs90}less able to do this kind of thing than him?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.19,0:35:24.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,我承认他会弹大键琴\N{\fs90}I mean, he can play the harpsichord
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.54,0:35:26.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,然而现在并没有什么卵用\N{\fs90}but that's not a skill we're gonna need today.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.31,0:35:29.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且他还中枪了\N{\fs90}And he's been shot
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.04,0:35:34.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,-詹姆斯 -干嘛\N{\fs90}-James. -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.39,0:35:36.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,-去把那辆雷诺偷来 -为什么\N{\fs90}-Go and steal that Renault over there. -Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.96,0:35:39.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为这是汽车节目 我们要有汽车元素\N{\fs90}Because this is a car show. We need a motoring element
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.67,0:35:40.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,有道理\N{\fs90}Good point
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.29,0:35:48.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,你觉得在这颗星球上 还有比他更不靠谱的吗\N{\fs90}Can you think of anybody on God's green Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.04,0:35:52.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,你觉得在这颗星球上 还有比他\N{\fs90}Can you think of anybody on God's green Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.37,0:35:56.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,你觉得在这颗星球上\N{\fs90}Can you think of anybody...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.71,0:35:58.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,你觉得\N{\fs90}Can you think...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.71,0:36:03.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯 你不能总是一遍遍做同样的事情啊\N{\fs90}James, you can't just keep doing the same thing over and over again
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.47,0:36:05.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 他一定会失手的\N{\fs90}Nah, he'll miss eventually
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.36,0:36:09.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,-噢天啊 -你看吧\N{\fs90}Oh, for God's sake. -There it is
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.11,0:36:14.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为老顽固下士不肯妥协\N{\fs90}Because Corporal Stubborn wouldn't budge from his tactic
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.56,0:36:17.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,理查德和我一致决定\N{\fs90}Richard and I decided that on our next attempt
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.24,0:36:20.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,下次我们要带点新装备参战\N{\fs90}we'd go into battle with some new equipment
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.56,0:36:24.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,去把那辆雷诺偷来\N{\fs90}Go and steal that Renault
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.52,0:36:47.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,去把那辆雷诺偷来\N{\fs90}Go and steal that Renault over there
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.54,0:37:08.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯 去把那辆雷诺偷来\N{\fs90}James, go and steal that Renault over there
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.32,0:37:10.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我不 -你什么意思\N{\fs90}No. -What do you mean, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.21,0:37:13.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,那边有个车库 里面肯定有车\N{\fs90}Well, there's a garage over there. It'll have some vehicles in it
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.62,0:37:14.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,对噢\N{\fs90}Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.14,0:37:20.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,这才像是汽车节目嘛\N{\fs90}Now we're in a car show
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.16,0:37:22.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,很好 杰里米你去解决那个狙击手\N{\fs90}Right, Jeremy, you go sort that sniper
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.41,0:37:23.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们来发动这些车\N{\fs90}we'll get these started
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.62,0:37:24.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,好主意\N{\fs90}Good plan
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.09,0:37:28.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,里面没有钥匙 我来搭线点火\N{\fs90}Right, there's no keys. I'll hotwire it
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.94,0:37:31.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢 他躲在那里\N{\fs90}Oh, there he is
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.74,0:37:36.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,和我的小伙伴问声好\N{\fs90}Say hello to my little friend
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.87,0:37:43.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,耶 这一枪如有神助\N{\fs90}Yes! What a shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.82,0:37:44.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.74,0:37:46.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,下次就没有这么好的准头了\N{\fs90}I'll never be able to do that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.51,0:37:48.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,-杰里米 -怎么了\N{\fs90}-Jeremy! -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.52,0:37:51.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯把自己电死了\N{\fs90}James has electrocuted himself
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.24,0:37:52.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,这蠢货\N{\fs90}Oh, what a...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.27,0:37:57.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,和我的小伙伴问声好\N{\fs90}Say hello to my little friend
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.36,0:38:01.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,里面没有钥匙 我来搭线点火\N{\fs90}Right, there are no keys. I'll hotwire it
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.06,0:38:03.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,你从来没看过电影吗\N{\fs90}Have you not seen every single movie ever made?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.59,0:38:19.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,没有放枪的地方 要给奥迪扣一分\N{\fs90}There's nowhere to put a gun. That is a bad mark for Audi
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.26,0:38:26.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,运动模式 关闭牵引力控制系统\N{\fs90}Sport, drive, traction control off
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.57,0:38:27.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,出发\N{\fs90}Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.54,0:38:48.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,难以置信\N{\fs90}Unbelievable
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.54,0:38:51.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,-杰里米 -怎么了\N{\fs90}Jeremy. -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.76,0:38:54.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,你的裤子为什么会掉\N{\fs90}Why did your trousers fall down?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.37,0:38:57.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为上面挂了太多手榴弹\N{\fs90}Because there were so many grenades attached to them
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.06,0:38:59.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,在直升机的倒灌风之下\N{\fs90}And in the down-draught of the helicopter...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.26,0:39:02.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,我可是很勇敢的 真的\N{\fs90}I was very brave doing that. I was
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.07,0:39:05.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我确定我看到他哭了 -那是勇敢的泪水\N{\fs90}-I'm sure I saw him crying. -They were tears of bravery
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.16,0:39:08.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢人们都这么说 勇敢的泪水\N{\fs90}Oh, that well-known expression. Tears of bravery
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.01,0:39:10.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,言归正传 在南非有那么一股潮流\N{\fs90}Anyway, look, there's a bit of a trend in South Africa
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.79,0:39:11.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,就是自己造车\N{\fs90}for making your own car
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.71,0:39:14.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,我是说从零打造一辆车 完全自己来\N{\fs90}making a car from scratch
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.97,0:39:16.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,举个例子\N{\fs90}We've got an example here
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.36,0:39:20.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,有人用一台宝马318i的引擎和一部分零件造出了这个\N{\fs90}This man's built this one based around the engineand a few bits from a BMW 318i
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.91,0:39:23.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,实话实说 看着还挺酷的\N{\fs90}And I've got to say, I think that's pretty cool
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.77,0:39:25.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,-真的不错 -还有很多这种例子\N{\fs90}It's brilliant. -There are lots of these
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.49,0:39:29.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,我更喜欢这台 同样使用了宝马的引擎 不过是V8\N{\fs90}I prefer this one, also with a BMW engine, a V8
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.01,0:39:31.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,可车身却是用牛仔布做的\N{\fs90}but the bodywork is made of denim
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.96,0:39:34.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,真是好审美啊\N{\fs90}A man of exquisite taste
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.02,0:39:36.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,但我认为其中最好的一台 简直太棒了\N{\fs90}I think the best of them all is so good
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.47,0:39:38.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,事实上我们把它请进了演播室\N{\fs90}we've actually brought it into the studio
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.82,0:39:40.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,大家看这里 真是难以置信的杰作\N{\fs90}Look, it's down here. Unbelievable, this
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.74,0:39:44.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是一台梅赛德斯奔驰C9的复制品\N{\fs90}It's a replica of a Mercedes C9
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.17,0:39:45.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 哈蒙德 就是它夺取了\N{\fs90}Now that, Hammond, was the car
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.71,0:39:50.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,1989年勒芒24小时耐力赛的冠军\N{\fs90}that won the 24-hour Le Mans race in 1989
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.29,0:39:53.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,实在是太棒了 我特地请来了它的制造者\N{\fs90}And it's so amazing, I've brought out the man who built it
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.27,0:39:56.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们 有请约翰 阿克曼\N{\fs90}Ladies and gentlemen, give him a warm hand. Johan Ackermann
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.56,0:39:58.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,感谢你的到来\N{\fs90}Thank you very much for coming
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.62,0:40:03.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,我能问一下\N{\fs90}Can I just as--
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.97,0:40:05.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,约翰 我能问一下吗\N{\fs90}Can I just ask, Johan
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.31,0:40:08.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,你是怎么打造出这些线条的\N{\fs90}how did you get the styling to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.78,0:40:10.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,嗯 杰里米 网上并没有这车的图样\N{\fs90}Well, Jeremy, there was no drawings on the internet
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.06,0:40:13.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以 我找了份写有比例的说明书\N{\fs90}so, erm... I got a book on the dimensions
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.92,0:40:17.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,但我找到最接近的也只是这1:32的模型\N{\fs90}but the closest I could get was a 1:32-scale model
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.15,0:40:19.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,等等 你是说先测量了模型\N{\fs90}Hang on, so you measured your toy car
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.59,0:40:23.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,把数据乘以32 然后造出这辆全尺寸的?\N{\fs90}multiplied it by 32 and built a full-sized one
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.27,0:40:24.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,-对 -真是这么造的啊\N{\fs90}-Yep. -That's how you did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.75,0:40:26.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,-可以合法上路吗 -完全合法\N{\fs90}-Is it road legal? -Fully road legal
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.93,0:40:29.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,-这不是模型 是真车吧  -没错\N{\fs90}-It's a real car, not a model? -Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.16,0:40:31.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,你造这车花了多久\N{\fs90}How long did you spend building this?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.14,0:40:33.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,从动工到完成 一共16个月\N{\fs90}From start to roadworthy was 16 months
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.97,0:40:36.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧 在这期间\N{\fs90}Right. Was there, or is there
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.46,0:40:38.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,你夫人有想过离婚吗\N{\fs90}a marriage to have survived this?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.77,0:40:40.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,希望她没有\N{\fs90}Well, I hope so
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.73,0:40:42.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,毕竟她还在现场 这应该是个好迹象\N{\fs90}My wife is here, so it must be a good sign
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.72,0:40:44.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,你好 耐心的女士\N{\fs90}Hello, patient lady
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.91,0:40:48.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,真了不起 干得漂亮\N{\fs90}Well, it's a remarkable achievement, and well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.22,0:40:49.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,请各位献上掌声吧 Johan Ackermann\N{\fs90}Ladies and gentlemen, Johan Ackermann
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.86,0:40:51.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,太赞了\N{\fs90}That's brilliant
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.23,0:40:59.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,接下来是一个全新的环节\N{\fs90}We're moving on to a great idea
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.74,0:41:02.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,完全是我和哈蒙德的原创\N{\fs90}that Richard Hammond and I have had all by our own
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.90,0:41:04.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,-而且真的很精彩  -确实\N{\fs90}-And it is brilliant.  -It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.42,0:41:09.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,请看——"詹姆斯梅 我们就是强你所难"\N{\fs90}It's called, Making James May Do Something He Doesn't Want To Do.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.38,0:41:12.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们将以画圈开头\N{\fs90}And we kick off with spinning
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.25,0:41:13.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是南非的特色 非常简单\N{\fs90}It's a South African thing. Fairly simple
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.95,0:41:16.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,先找辆上了年纪的后驱车\N{\fs90}You get an elderly rear-wheel-drive car
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.30,0:41:17.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,开到一个停车场\N{\fs90}take it to a car park where you do doughnuts in it
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.39,0:41:21.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,伴着节奏感极强的说唱  漂移画圈圈\N{\fs90}to a backdrop of strong rap music
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.46,0:41:25.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,这活动集活力 趣味 年轻化 于一体\N{\fs90}It's lively, it's interesting, and it's youthful
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.08,0:41:27.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,完全就是他的对立面\N{\fs90}It's everything he isn't
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.83,0:41:47.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,就是这了\N{\fs90}Well, here we are, then
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.69,0:41:50.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,Jo'burg的最佳转圈场地\N{\fs90}at one of Jo'burg's top spinning destinations,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.99,0:41:54.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,人们形象地称之为'车轮与浓烟的禁地'\N{\fs90}the aptly-named Wheelz 'n' Smoke Arena
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.68,0:41:56.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,这种活动的意义在于\N{\fs90}And the object of the exercise
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.35,0:41:57.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,要我说\N{\fs90}as far as I can make out
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.75,0:41:59.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,就是为了拉烟\N{\fs90}is to create smoke
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.55,0:42:05.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,在场内一圈一圈的转\N{\fs90}And drive round and round the arena
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.02,0:42:06.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,直到爆胎\N{\fs90}until the tyres go bang
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.28,0:42:10.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,而破轮胎的残骸\N{\fs90}And then what's left of the tyres
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.97,0:42:12.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,会丢进那边的火堆\N{\fs90}are put on a bonfire over there
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.46,0:42:14.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是为了保证轮胎完全无残留\N{\fs90}to make sure there's absolutely nothing left
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.79,0:42:28.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是史黛西 我猜 她今年才17岁\N{\fs90}This is Stacy, and she's only about 17, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.68,0:42:31.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,坊间传闻以及群众们的欢呼声\N{\fs90}And the word round here and the noise in the crowd
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.50,0:42:33.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,都表明史黛西是个中高手\N{\fs90}says that Stacy is actually very good at this
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.66,0:42:36.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,但我不确定啊 眼前尽是白烟\N{\fs90}But how the bloody hell would I know? It's just a massive cloud of smoke...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.16,0:42:41.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,偶尔模糊地看到头灯\N{\fs90}...with some headlights occasionally appearing in it
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.92,0:42:45.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,为了帮助我理解这项活动的意义\N{\fs90}To help me get into the spirit of things
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.01,0:42:48.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,举办者们觉得我应该亲身经历一下\N{\fs90}the organisers suggested I should become more involved
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.18,0:42:54.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.62,0:43:02.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,伙计 快看转速表 一直在红区里\N{\fs90}Look at the rev case, in the red constantly, mate
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.02,0:43:07.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,我并不喜欢晚上胎烟的味道\N{\fs90}I don't like the smell of tyre smoke in the evening
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.41,0:43:10.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,喂 快回来\N{\fs90}Oi! Get back in!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.15,0:43:14.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,回到车里来 你***的\N{\fs90}Get back in the car, you [BLEEP] idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.97,0:43:17.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,救命\N{\fs90}Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.46,0:43:27.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs90}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.01,0:43:41.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,-爆了没  -爆了\N{\fs90}-Has it broken?  -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.79,0:43:42.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,终于\N{\fs90}Finally.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.68,0:44:02.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,之前我车上的轮胎\N{\fs90}I got 20,000 miles
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.06,0:44:04.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,足足开了32,000公里呢\N{\fs90}out of the last set of rear tyres on my car
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.04,0:44:36.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,鼓起勇气开一轮啊\N{\fs90}Just go out there and do it
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.38,0:44:37.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,想想如果在英国这么玩\N{\fs90}Fancy trying to do that in England
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.79,0:44:39.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,或者任何地方 比如澳大利亚\N{\fs90}Or anywhere. Or Australia
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.67,0:44:40.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,不管怎么说 咳咳\N{\fs90}Anyway, mm-mm-mm
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.47,0:44:44.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯 当时你享受过哪怕一秒钟吗\N{\fs90}James May, was there any part of that that you enjoyed?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.12,0:44:45.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,-没有  -很好\N{\fs90}Nope.  -Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.66,0:44:50.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在到了明星脑碰脑环节\N{\fs90}But now it is time for Celebrity Brain Crash
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.20,0:44:59.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,自从上周发生的不幸之后\N{\fs90}Now after what happened last week
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.15,0:45:03.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,这周的嘉宾拒绝\N{\fs90}our guest this week declined our offer
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.41,0:45:04.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,乘坐气垫船出场\N{\fs90}to arrive at the studio on a hovercraft,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.87,0:45:06.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,她表示宁愿步行\N{\fs90}saying she would prefer to walk
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.66,0:45:08.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,-这可以理解  -是的\N{\fs90}-It's understandable.  -Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.63,0:45:10.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,我肯定 尽管如此\N{\fs90}I'm sure that despite this
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.22,0:45:12.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,你们还是会热烈欢迎这位嘉宾\N{\fs90}you will still give her an enormous welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.44,0:45:15.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为 虽然她现在已是好莱坞大咖\N{\fs90}Although she's now a major Hollywood star
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.65,0:45:18.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,但她出生在这 南非\N{\fs90}She was actually born here in South Africa
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.72,0:45:21.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们 有请查理兹塞隆\N{\fs90}Ladies and gentlemen, please welcome Charlize Theron!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.02,0:45:27.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,一定要问她有关"死在西部的一百万种方式"的问题\N{\fs90}We must ask her about A Million Ways To Die In The West.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.50,0:45:29.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,我超喜欢那电影\N{\fs90}I love that film.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.18,0:45:31.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,但我最喜欢的是她在里面的造型\N{\fs90}But what I really love is the way she looks in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.74,0:45:35.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,帽子和飘飘的裙摆 而且她骑着自行车\N{\fs90}The hat and the floaty skirt. She's on a bicycle as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.45,0:45:42.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,-不是吧  -我的天\N{\fs90}Oh, no. Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.23,0:45:45.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,-别...  -女士们先生们\N{\fs90}- Oh, not...  -Ladies and gentlemen
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.32,0:45:48.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,查理兹塞隆被一头狮子攻击了\N{\fs90}Charlize Theron has been attacked by a lion
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.66,0:45:50.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,-不要啊  -我们确实无能为力\N{\fs90}- Oh, no.  -Literally nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.83,0:45:54.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以说她来不了吗\N{\fs90}Does that mean she's not coming on, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.27,0:45:56.93,字幕,,0,0,0,,她被狮子吃啦\N{\fs90}She's been eaten by a lion.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.13,0:46:00.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧 也许观众中\N{\fs90}Well, look, are there any other well-known
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.31,0:46:02.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,有著名的南非明星\N{\fs90}South Africans in the audience?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.21,0:46:03.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,这不太可能 詹姆斯\N{\fs90}It's not very likely, James
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.26,0:46:05.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,世界上有名的南非人就两个\N{\fs90}There's only two globally famous South Africans
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.23,0:46:08.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,一个在狮子肚子里 还有一个在监狱里\N{\fs90}One's now in a lion and the other's in prison
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.31,0:46:11.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,那么 回到之前的话题吧\N{\fs90}Let's get back to what we were doing
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.54,0:46:15.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,早些时候 我们在一个约旦特种部队训练基地\N{\fs90}Earlier on, we were at a Jordanian special forces training base
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.41,0:46:17.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,学习如何成为超级士兵\N{\fs90}learning to be super army soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.31,0:46:21.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,接下来我们要冲向一架被劫持的客机\N{\fs90}And we pick up the action as we rush towards the hijacked airliner
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.76,0:46:25.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,营救VIP 并护送至安全点\N{\fs90}to rescue a VIP and take them to safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.90,0:46:39.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,容我解释这个计划\N{\fs90}Let me talk you through the plan
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.68,0:46:43.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯和理查德将开着餐车作为突击车\N{\fs90}James and Richard will use the catering lorry as an assault vehicle
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.23,0:46:47.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,然后 我们救到VIP之后\N{\fs90}And then, after we've rescued the VIP
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.16,0:46:51.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,再驾驶奥迪跑路\N{\fs90}we'll use the Audi as a getaway car
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.42,0:46:58.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们现在要机智地\N{\fs90}Now what we're doing here, very cleverly
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.79,0:47:00.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,从飞机后面绕过去\N{\fs90}is we're going round the back of the plane
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.80,0:47:04.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为飞机没有后视窗或反光镜\N{\fs90}because planes don't have rear windows or door mirrors
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.98,0:47:06.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以他们看不见我们在潜行\N{\fs90}so they won't see us sneaking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.71,0:47:08.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,多隐秘啊\N{\fs90}Stealthy, you see
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.08,0:47:12.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德 我们溜过去\N{\fs90}Hammond, we're manoeuvring in
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.44,0:47:14.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,-好的  -按下气刹\N{\fs90}-OK.  -Dab the brakes
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.27,0:47:19.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,好了 我们已就位\N{\fs90}Right, we are in position
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.43,0:47:23.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯会把我抬到门边\N{\fs90}James is gonna lift me on this platform to the door
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.24,0:47:25.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,然后我们突击\N{\fs90}then we go in
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.49,0:47:27.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,你准备好了吗\N{\fs90}Right, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.12,0:47:29.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,我准备好放下千斤顶了\N{\fs90}I'm ready to lower the jacks
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.16,0:47:31.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,简直太隐蔽了\N{\fs90}Absolute stealth
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.88,0:47:45.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,我认为那些恐怖分子\N{\fs90}I think the terrorists
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.48,0:47:47.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,会注意到的\N{\fs90}are going to notice this assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.66,0:48:09.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,我认为恐怖分子们会注意到的\N{\fs90}I think the terrorists are going to notice this assault
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.21,0:48:12.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,因此我要转移他们的注意力\N{\fs90}Which is why I shall now cause a diversion
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.24,0:48:19.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,我要在飞机前面画圆拉烟\N{\fs90}I'm gonna make a smoking doughnut in front of the plane
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.10,0:48:20.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,来让恐怖分子分心\N{\fs90}to distract the terrorists
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.00,0:48:26.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,不好 简直太糟糕了\N{\fs90}Oh, no, this is a disaster
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.64,0:48:29.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,即使你把电子牵引力系统关了\N{\fs90}Even when you turn the traction control off
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.39,0:48:31.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,也无济于事\N{\fs90}it isn't fully off
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.01,0:48:35.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,你只好忍受这漫长无趣的转向不足\N{\fs90}so you just get miles and miles of dreary understeer
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.99,0:48:37.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,这点给奥迪差评\N{\fs90}Bad mark for Audi here
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.50,0:48:42.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,给点力\N{\fs90}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.17,0:48:45.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,唯一的好处是\N{\fs90}The only good thing is
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.36,0:48:47.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,恐怖分子们确实能透过窗户看到\N{\fs90}the terrorists will be looking out of the cockpit windows
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.58,0:48:51.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,还会纳闷 为啥奥迪这么转向不足\N{\fs90}thinking, "Why is that Audi understeering around like that?"
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.20,0:48:53.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,好的 趴下\N{\fs90}Right! Go low!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.22,0:49:02.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,我来了\N{\fs90}Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.00,0:49:06.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,为转向不足的破坏而道歉\N{\fs90}Cry havoc and let slip the dog of understeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.99,0:49:06.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1920,152)}莎翁名言 原句为战争的破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.03,0:49:24.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,两位 我找到VIP了\N{\fs90}Chaps, I have located the VIP
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.27,0:49:26.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,她就是英国女王\N{\fs90}and it is the Queen of England
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.49,0:49:28.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢皇室\N{\fs90}I don't like the Royal Family
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.24,0:49:32.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯 现在不是表达你共和言论的时候\N{\fs90}James, now is not the time for your republican views
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.75,0:49:35.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,陛下 我们是精英作战小组\N{\fs90}Ma'am, we are an elite fighting force
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.79,0:49:38.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们外面停着奥迪 马上\N{\fs90}We have an Audi outside. We will...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.65,0:49:44.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,你为什么对哈蒙德开枪\N{\fs90}Why did you shoot Hammond?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.00,0:49:45.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,他太烦人了\N{\fs90}He was being annoying
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.57,0:49:51.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,就这么干\N{\fs90}That's how you do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.86,0:49:58.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,夫人 我们是精英作战小组\N{\fs90}Ma'am, we are an elite fighting force
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.75,0:50:01.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们外面停着奥迪 马上\N{\fs90}We have an Audi outside. We will...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.03,0:50:08.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,-你朝詹姆斯开枪了-他先动手的\N{\fs90}-Did you shoot May?  -Well, he shot me!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.18,0:50:15.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,就这么干\N{\fs90}That's how you do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.70,0:50:17.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,然而在下一次尝试中\N{\fs90}Somehow in our next attempt
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.36,0:50:19.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德跑到了机翼上\N{\fs90}Hammond ended up on the wing
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.86,0:50:25.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦 你想玩传统的啊\N{\fs90}Oh, I see. You wanna do this the old-fashioned way
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.68,0:50:29.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,好啊 就陪你玩玩\N{\fs90}OK, let's dance
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.04,0:50:41.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,夫人 我们是精英作战小组\N{\fs90}Ma'am, we are an elite fighting force.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.93,0:50:45.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,外面停着奥迪 会带您去安全地带\N{\fs90}We have an Audi waiting outside to get you to safety
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.46,0:50:47.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,-那你是做什么的 -我说了\N{\fs90}And what do you do?  -I just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.76,0:50:49.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们是精英作战小组\N{\fs90}We are an elite fighting force
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.79,0:50:52.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,外面停着奥迪 会带您去安全地带\N{\fs90}We have an Audi waiting outside to get you to safety
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.42,0:50:54.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,-您会喜欢的 德系 -就像您一样\N{\fs90}You'll like it, it's German.  -Like you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.83,0:50:58.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,谢了 詹姆斯 后面的恐怖分子死光了吗\N{\fs90}Thank you, James. Are all the terrorists dead back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.09,0:50:59.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,-后面所有人都死了 -好样的\N{\fs90}-Everybody's dead back there.  -Good man
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.79,0:51:01.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,陛下 请跟我来\N{\fs90}Your Majesty, if you'd like to follow us
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.12,0:51:13.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,又怎么了\N{\fs90}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.66,0:51:15.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,他刚朝女王后脑勺开了一枪\N{\fs90}He's just shot the Queen in the back of the head
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.85,0:51:17.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,额 接下来怎么办\N{\fs90}Well, now what we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.03,0:51:21.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦 次奥
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.64,0:51:28.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,上车吧 这个我来保管 谢谢\N{\fs90}Go. I'll have that, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.82,0:51:33.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,终于把女王带上了车\N{\fs90}Having finally got the Queen into the car
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.26,0:51:36.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们驶向通往大使馆的危险之路\N{\fs90}we were now faced with a perilous drive to the embassy
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.68,0:51:42.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,不过 这也意味我能干回老本行了\N{\fs90}However, this did at least mean I could get back to my day job
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.78,0:51:48.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,好好聊聊这车 这是S8 plus\N{\fs90}I'll talk you through the car. This is the S8 Plus
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.61,0:51:53.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,plus的意思是比标准版多80匹马力\N{\fs90}Plus means it has 80 more horsepower than the standard car
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.35,0:51:57.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,也就是说百公里加速仅需3.8秒\N{\fs90}That means 0-60 in 3.8 seconds
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.23,0:52:00.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,极速 304km/h\N{\fs90}top speed: 190
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.43,0:52:01.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,挺有意思\N{\fs90}How very interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.87,0:52:09.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,驯服这猛兽靠的不光是全时四驱\N{\fs90}The immense power is harnessed not only by all-wheel drive
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.52,0:52:12.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,还有陶瓷刹车\N{\fs90}but also by ceramic brakes
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.16,0:52:16.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,还有电子差速器\N{\fs90}And an electronic differential
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.18,0:52:19.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,这可不是聊车的时候啊哥们\N{\fs90}There's a time and a place for talking about that stuff, mate!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.16,0:52:21.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,坐在一个1米96的司机后面\N{\fs90}Sitting behind a six-foot-five-inch driver
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.62,0:52:24.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,意味着后排腿部空间好不到哪去\N{\fs90}means that rear leg room is rather at a premium.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.33,0:52:25.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,话虽这么说\N{\fs90}Having said that
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.62,0:52:27.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,作为辆高性能四门车\N{\fs90}however, for a high-performance saloon
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.35,0:52:29.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,舒适度是相当可以的\N{\fs90}the ride quality is really rather good
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.35,0:52:31.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,你俩能不能别评测车了\N{\fs90}Will you two stop reviewing the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.10,0:52:36.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,女王大人您有什么看法\N{\fs90}Do you have an opinion, the Queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.72,0:52:37.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在不是时候啊\N{\fs90}Not now!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.10,0:52:43.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,开稳点 我要射他们\N{\fs90}Hold it steady, I'm gonna shoot them
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.30,0:52:50.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,射他的脸啊\N{\fs90}Shoot him in the face!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.08,0:52:52.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,你是远道而来吗\N{\fs90}Have you come far?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.88,0:53:02.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,007黎明生机 非常人贩2和3 飓风营救 冷血悍将\N{\fs90}The Living Daylights. Transporter 2 and 3 Taken Ronin
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.08,0:53:03.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,你为啥要列举电影啊\N{\fs90}Why are you listing films?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.53,0:53:08.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,每部电影里都有大奥迪飞驰的身影啊\N{\fs90}Because all those films had a big Audi saloon in them going quickly
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.72,0:53:12.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,好莱坞英雄座驾的不二之选\N{\fs90}It is the car of choice for the Hollywood hero
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.05,0:53:13.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,闭嘴\N{\fs90}Shut up
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.58,0:53:19.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯 那玩意极速多少\N{\fs90}What's the top speed of that thing, James?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.82,0:53:21.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,不到150km/h吧\N{\fs90}About 90 miles an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.43,0:53:26.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,那么 给好莱坞英雄们一个忠告\N{\fs90}Well, here is a top tip for Hollywood heroes
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.08,0:53:31.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,要是追你的车跑不快\N{\fs90}If you're being chased by a car which is slower than the car you're in
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.06,0:53:33.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,只需要开的比它快就行\N{\fs90}simply drive faster than it
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.19,0:53:39.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,凯奇拍勇闯夺命岛的时候就该好好想想\N{\fs90}See, that's what Nick Cage ought to have thought about, really, in The Rock
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.52,0:53:43.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,还有热血悍将里那位 开着S8追雪铁龙\N{\fs90}And that man in Ronin, with the S8 chasing the Citroen
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.16,0:53:45.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,别再说电影情节了\N{\fs90}Stop talking about films!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.64,0:53:47.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,有个大家伙逼近我们了\N{\fs90}There's a bogey waxing our tail
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.54,0:53:49.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,-天啊 -我要打它油箱\N{\fs90}-Oh, God!  -Gonna shoot its petrol tank
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.87,0:53:52.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯 打油箱没用的\N{\fs90}James, there's no point shooting it
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.26,0:53:54.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,汽油只会在电影里爆炸\N{\fs90}Petrol only blows up in films
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.88,0:54:04.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧 凡事皆有例外\N{\fs90}Well, that's not strictly accurate
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.75,0:54:07.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,-那天杀的大使馆在哪 -往前走\N{\fs90}-Where the bloody hell is the embassy?  -Go down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.80,0:54:11.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,-扯淡 -到了到了\N{\fs90}-No, this is rubbish.  -There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.28,0:54:12.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,终于到了\N{\fs90}There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.74,0:54:15.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,好 你们带女王去安全的地方\N{\fs90}Right, you get the Queen to safety
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.61,0:54:17.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,我掩护你们\N{\fs90}I'll cover you
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.15,0:54:20.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,-交给我 -好了 快跑 跑啊\N{\fs90}-OK, I'm on it.  -Right, good. Go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.58,0:54:23.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,陛下 咱们得快点 非常快\N{\fs90}Really quickly, Your Majesty
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.66,0:54:27.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们看不见了\N{\fs90}We can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.60,0:54:44.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,杰里米 快过来 过来啊\N{\fs90}Come on, Jeremy, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.84,0:54:46.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,我已经尽力跑了\N{\fs90}I'm doing my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.03,0:54:50.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,正中靶心\N{\fs90}In the plums!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.86,0:54:53.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,别停 接着跑\N{\fs90}Oh, no! Just keep moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.23,0:54:57.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,又来一次\N{\fs90}They've done it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.09,0:55:00.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯 你要错过这了\N{\fs90}James, you're missing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.15,0:55:02.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,您不能把皇权现代化\N{\fs90}You cannot modernise the royalty
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.49,0:55:05.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为它充其量\N{\fs90}because royalty is, at the very best
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.21,0:55:06.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,就是个中世纪的概念\N{\fs90}a medieval concept
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.96,0:55:10.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,啊 开枪啊\N{\fs90}Oh! Shooting!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.26,0:55:13.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,又来了一枪 他还在跑\N{\fs90}That's gonna sting! He's still coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.34,0:55:14.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,别停 继续跑\N{\fs90}Keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.72,0:55:16.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,小心地雷\N{\fs90}Mind the mines!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.24,0:55:24.19,字幕,,0,0,0,,他还在跑\N{\fs90}He's still going!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.39,0:55:48.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯 他死了\N{\fs90}James, he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.23,0:55:53.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,等等 他动了 又动起来了\N{\fs90}No, wait a minute. He's going again! He's moving again!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.24,0:55:55.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,加油杰里米 你能做到\N{\fs90}Jeremy, come on, you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.32,0:55:57.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,加油加油 接着爬\N{\fs90}Come on, keep going! Come on
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.87,0:55:59.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,-就差一点了 -哈蒙德\N{\fs90}-This is it.  -Hammond...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.59,0:56:00.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,终点就在眼前了\N{\fs90}There's the finish line!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.84,0:56:02.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,我没走错吧\N{\fs90}Am I going the right way?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.54,0:56:05.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,差不多了 滚过来吧 你行的\N{\fs90}More or less. Roll over it. You can do it
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.66,0:56:08.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们成功了\N{\fs90}Yes! We have done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.48,0:56:14.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,你是远道而来吗\N{\fs90}Have you come far?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.29,0:56:27.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,非常不可思议的作战小组\N{\fs90}A fighting force. An unbelievable fighting force
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.00,0:56:34.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们花9小时48分完成了这个演习\N{\fs90}We actually managed to complete that course in nine hours and 48 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.31,0:56:38.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,只比真正的军人慢了9个半小时\N{\fs90}And that's only nine-and-a-half hours slower than the actual soldiers
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.22,0:56:41.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,我能问下 你到底挨了多少枪\N{\fs90}Can I just ask, how many times were you shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.24,0:56:43.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,-冲刺时吗 -往大使馆跑的那段\N{\fs90}What, on the run in?  -On the way to the embassy
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.32,0:56:47.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,17枪打到身上 2枪打到了蛋蛋边\N{\fs90}Er... 17 to the torso, two to the... plum set
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.75,0:56:49.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,你居然还活着\N{\fs90}And you lived?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.91,0:56:52.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,当然 詹姆斯你看 我活下来了\N{\fs90}Well, obviously, James, yes, look, I lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.16,0:56:54.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,确实活下来了 伴随着这糟糕的失望之情\N{\fs90}He did. And on that terrible disappointment
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.89,0:56:56.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,我想是结束的时候了\N{\fs90}it is time to end
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.08,0:56:57.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,是的 感谢收看\N{\fs90}Yes, it is. Thank you so much for watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.94,0:57:00.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,下周我们在别处再相见 拜拜\N{\fs90}See you somewhere next week. Goodbye!
